  "ai_usage": "Use for nostalgic/retro projects or anniversary pages evoking 2005–2008. The 'gloss' is a top-half white-to-transparent gradient overlaid on a colored gradient; reflective buttons stack two gradients. Recolor via --sky/--lime. Keep it tongue-in-cheek. Modern semantics/contrast are preserved so it stays usable.",
